"Drah!"  Quickstrike grunted as a beam struck him leaving a burnt stop
on his torse.  He ignored the pain best he could and fired a beam of
cyber venom from his snake mouth at Nightstrike.

Inferno saw his chance and aimed his gun with a twisted grin on his
face. He pulled the trigger launching a rocket at Darkfate.
